  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@Haroenv As said in the description, the main search box is part of the demo style (next PR).\r\n\r\n> opacity of the \"active\" clear filters is too low I think\r\n\r\nThat's part of Nico's design but I agree. I think we should do a pass later on accessibility.\r\n\r\n> triangle for the hierarchical menu should be pointing rightwards instead of upwards when disabled\r\n\r\nI didn't style the design that we didn't receive yet but that's a good idea I think.\r\n\r\n> because the visual height of the slider is smaller, the touch target became somewhat too small now\r\n\r\nWell spotted! I usually only use the handlers.\r\n\r\n> images aren't the same height\r\n\r\nThis is part of next PR. The hits are specific to the demo.",
